These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Game: go, scrabble, whist, poker
Sport: cycling, ice-hockey, soccer, weightlifting
1. Game:go is on the right of Sport:soccer##1
2. Sport:weightlifting is on the far left##1
3. Sport:soccer is between Sport:ice-hockey and Game:scrabble##2
4. Game:poker is on the far left##1
5. Game:whist is between Game:scrabble and Game:go##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Game   | poker         | scrabble   | whist | go       |
| Sport      | weightlifting | cycling | soccer   | ice-hockey |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
Flower: balloon-flower, poppy, daffodil, bellflower
1. Flower:bellflower is between Hobby:reading and Flower:poppy##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. Flower:daffodil is on the right of Flower:balloon-flower##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of Flower:balloon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| Flower   | poppy    | bellflower   | balloon-flower | daffodil       |

