2. House:palace is between House:tower and Food:corn##2
3. House:tower is on the far left##1
4. House:victorian is on the left of Food:cranberry##1
5. Food:corn == House:victorian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food          | kale    | cauliflower | corn   | cranberry  |
| House   | tower | palace   | victorian | cottage |

